{"id":"the-seed-bank-of-winter","slug":"the-seed-bank-of-winter","title":"The Seed Bank of Winter","title_ko":"겨울 씨앗 은행","level":"B1","ageBand":"11-13","coverUrl":"/seed/the-seed-bank-of-winter/cover.webp","summary_ko":"혹독한 겨울에 씨앗을 지키려는 아이들이 마을 씨앗 은행을 만들며 다음 봄을 준비하는 이야기예요.","wordCount":269,"pages":[{"id":"the-seed-bank-of-winter-p1","pageNo":1,"spread":"p1","imageUrl":"/seed/the-seed-bank-of-winter/p1.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-seed-bank-of-winter-p1-s1","ord":0,"text":"That winter, the snow came early and stayed like a closed door. Gardens vanished under white drifts before many families had saved seeds.","translation_ko":"그해 겨울 눈은 일찍 와서 닫힌 문처럼 머물렀어요. 많은 가족이 씨앗을 모으기도 전에 정원은 하얀 눈더미 아래 사라졌어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-seed-bank-of-winter/audio/p1-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"That","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":300},{"word":"winter","charStart":5,"charEnd":11,"startMs":300,"endMs":620},{"word":"the","charStart":13,"charEnd":16,"startMs":960,"endMs":1100},{"word":"snow","charStart":17,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1100,"endMs":1240},{"word":"came","charStart":22,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1240,"endMs":1540},{"word":"early","charStart":27,"charEnd":32,"startMs":1540,"endMs":1900},{"word":"and","charStart":33,"charEnd":36,"startMs":1900,"endMs":2400},{"word":"stayed","charStart":37,"charEnd":43,"startMs":2400,"endMs":2640},{"word":"like","charStart":44,"charEnd":48,"startMs":2640,"endMs":2820},{"word":"a","charStart":49,"charEnd":50,"startMs":2820,"endMs":3080},{"word":"closed","charStart":51,"charEnd":57,"startMs":3080,"endMs":3360},{"word":"door","charStart":58,"charEnd":62,"startMs":3360,"endMs":3700},{"word":"Gardens","charStart":64,"charEnd":71,"startMs":4900,"endMs":4900},{"word":"vanished","charStart":72,"charEnd":80,"startMs":4900,"endMs":5320},{"word":"under","charStart":81,"charEnd":86,"startMs":5320,"endMs":5640},{"word":"white","charStart":87,"charEnd":92,"startMs":5640,"endMs":5980},{"word":"drifts","charStart":93,"charEnd":99,"startMs":5980,"endMs":6320},{"word":"before","charStart":100,"charEnd":106,"startMs":6320,"endMs":6860},{"word":"many","charStart":107,"charEnd":111,"startMs":6860,"endMs":7220},{"word":"families","charStart":112,"charEnd":120,"startMs":7220,"endMs":7580},{"word":"had","charStart":121,"charEnd":124,"startMs":7580,"endMs":7860},{"word":"saved","charStart":125,"charEnd":130,"startMs":7860,"endMs":8140},{"word":"seeds","charStart":131,"charEnd":136,"startMs":8140,"endMs":8500}]}]},{"id":"the-seed-bank-of-winter-p2","pageNo":2,"spread":"p2","imageUrl":"/seed/the-seed-bank-of-winter/p2.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-seed-bank-of-winter-p2-s1","ord":0,"text":"My teacher worried that spring would arrive to empty packets and forgotten names. She unlocked the village hall and spread brown paper across the tables.","translation_ko":"선생님은 봄이 빈 봉투와 잊힌 이름들 앞에 올까 봐 걱정하셨어요. 선생님은 마을 회관 문을 열고 탁자 위에 갈색 종이를 펼쳤어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-seed-bank-of-winter/audio/p2-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"My","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":240},{"word":"teacher","charStart":3,"charEnd":10,"startMs":240,"endMs":580},{"word":"worried","charStart":11,"charEnd":18,"startMs":580,"endMs":1000},{"word":"that","charStart":19,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1000,"endMs":1340},{"word":"spring","charStart":24,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1340,"endMs":1560},{"word":"would","charStart":31,"charEnd":36,"startMs":1560,"endMs":1780},{"word":"arrive","charStart":37,"charEnd":43,"startMs":1780,"endMs":2060},{"word":"to","charStart":44,"charEnd":46,"startMs":2060,"endMs":2380},{"word":"empty","charStart":47,"charEnd":52,"startMs":2380,"endMs":2620},{"word":"packets","charStart":53,"charEnd":60,"startMs":2620,"endMs":3020},{"word":"and","charStart":61,"charEnd":64,"startMs":3020,"endMs":3280},{"word":"forgotten","charStart":65,"charEnd":74,"startMs":3280,"endMs":3680},{"word":"names","charStart":75,"charEnd":80,"startMs":3680,"endMs":4100},{"word":"She","charStart":82,"charEnd":85,"startMs":4640,"endMs":4800},{"word":"unlocked","charSta